<p class=MsoNormal style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt'><span lang=EN-US>4</span>．<span lang=EN-US>Radio Source</span>，短押<span lang=EN-US>[VR]Softkey</span>，再短押<span lang=EN-US>[Help]Softkey</span>迁移至<span lang=EN-US>[VR Help]</span>画面，快速来回短押<span lang=EN-US>REV</span>和<span lang=EN-US>IG</span>，重复上述手顺，进入<span lang=EN-US>[VR

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt'><span lang=EN-US> <o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt'>这个问题<span lang=EN-US>UI</span>本地再现了下，再现率大概是<span lang=EN-US> 1/10.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt'>看了下<span lang=EN-US>log</span>，请求<span lang=EN-US>camera </span>启动后，<span lang=EN-US>UI</span>停止了文件节点<span lang=EN-US> check </span>的<span lang=EN-US>timer</span>。然后等<span lang=EN-US>rspSourceChange
</span>消息。<span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt'>等到的<span lang=EN-US> cameraService </span>的<span lang=EN-US> rspSourceChange</span>消息参数是：<span lang=EN-US>PREVIEW_STATUS_DO_NOT_USE</span>，所以画面一直卡住。<span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt'><span lang=EN-US>4</span>．<span lang=EN-US>Radio Source</span>，短押<span lang=EN-US>[VR]Softkey</span>，再短押<span lang=EN-US>[Help]Softkey</span>迁移至<span lang=EN-US>[VR Help]</span>画面，快速来回短押<span lang=EN-US>REV</span>和<span lang=EN-US>IG</span>，重复上述手顺，进入<span lang=EN-US>[VR

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt'><span lang=EN-US> <o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt'>这个问题<span lang=EN-US>UI</span>本地再现了下，再现率大概是<span lang=EN-US> 1/10.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt'>看了下<span lang=EN-US>log</span>，请求<span lang=EN-US>camera </span>启动后，<span lang=EN-US>UI</span>停止了文件节点<span lang=EN-US> check </span>的<span lang=EN-US>timer</span>。然后等<span lang=EN-US>rspSourceChange
</span>消息。<span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt'>等到的<span lang=EN-US> cameraService </span>的<span lang=EN-US> rspSourceChange</span>消息参数是：<span lang=EN-US>PREVIEW_STATUS_DO_NOT_USE</span>，所以画面一直卡住。<span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></p>
